{"tid":151574,"cid":31,"subCid":0,"title":"人民入境事務處又打黎","createTime":"2017-03-11T04:00:57.000Z","updateTime":"2017-03-12T00:04:07.000Z","uid":67957,"like":0,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"0703c3237eda029af555ec88b48b0fa6daf175ef","tid":151574,"uid":67957,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-11T04:00:57.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/7U8Z56X.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F7U8Z56X.jpg&h=520603c3&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n重要留言比人<img src=\"/assets/faces/big/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"94729873930ea8a76baf2165ee34f5664e76e072","tid":151574,"uid":66951,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-11T04:05:05.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n擺粒膠響度以為笑人巧威威<br />\n<br />\n但乜point都冇提出<br />\n<br />\n憑咩去話人<br />\n<br />\n尤其是係呢d真係正經討論ge post<br />\n<br />\n真係想見到大家有誠意咁去就一個題目發表自己意見<br />\n<br />\n唔係擺粒膠響度&hellip;自命清高咁笑人"},{"pid":"2b0272a4e055811511673d6d16e78238c26de5c6","tid":151574,"uid":24785,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-11T04:08:46.000Z","msg":"都係錄音電話黎架啦，唔係咩?<br />\n應該唔係特登留言"},{"pid":"412031dd34d87f886782c583f123d8ea98b7eeff","tid":151574,"uid":67957,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-11T04:26:31.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>都係錄音電話黎架啦，唔係咩?<br />\n應該唔係特登留言</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n當初以為唔識既人打黎，我冇聽，之後又電話留言比我，一聽原來係假入境處。前果幾秒有人聲，之後先播錄音"},{"pid":"5fc560cdf7979e8beb6c4bfeb13ae27e0ebd31ad","tid":151574,"uid":61987,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-11T18:01:36.000Z","msg":"我前幾日都收到一見到852就即刻收線<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"2ea2db34f0d222f5c0020951d9b2ce9b4147ffdd","tid":151574,"uid":19521,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-12T00:00:45.000Z","msg":"<im